 月 12 日<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-iphone-15-event-is-set-for-september-12th-161028116.html">iPhone 活动的</a>一部分，苹果可能会用新的 USB-C 充电盒更新 AirPods Pro。（当前的 AirPods Pro 充电盒使用 Lightning 接口。）新款 iPhone <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-iphone-15-event-is-set-for-september-12th-161028116.html">应该会更换</a>也可连接至 USB-C，因此，如果您更喜欢更新的端口，那么值得等待。也就是说，预计 AirPods Pro 的实际硬件不会有其他变化，并且 USB-C 型号的起步价格可能会高于此折扣价格。这款耳机将在今年晚些时候获得新功能，但这些功能将基于软件，iOS 17 会添加<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-adaptive-audio-for-airpods-tunes-anc-and-transparency-to-your-environment-181218028.html">新的“自适应音频”模式</a>和更快的设备切换等升级。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-pro-are-back-down-to-199-150816670.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-pro-are-back-down-to-199-150816670.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0f8bb13a-3a7f-4b5c-92ca-b73d2e5cc0ea</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 15:08:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694012898</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T15:08:29+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Audio Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><med