chantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdhG_iCSoAIceyX6la7Nk0hQDpfOpMRLy4QdGscFawY-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-bans-iphone-use-for-government-officials-at-work-635fe2f8" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.wsj.com/world/china/china-bans-iphone-use-for-government-officials-at-work-635fe2f8"><em>《华尔街日报》</em></a>报道，中国扩大了对政府官员使用 iPhone 和其他进口设备的禁令。据“知情人士”称，据报道，政府雇员在聊天群和会议上被告知不要将外国品牌设备带入办公室或在工作中使用它们。据报道，此举的目的是减少对外国技术的依赖并提高网络安全。</p><p>如果你有<em>似曾相识的</em>感觉，那是因为北京此前曾将苹果和其他外国产品列入政府部门的黑名单，最近一次<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-12-09-china-bans-all-government-departments-from-using-us-made-technol.html">是在 2019 年</a>。当时，政府计划在三年内逐步淘汰西方装备，转而采用本地替代品。当时的目标是将数据保留在境内，并确保技术“安全”和“可控”，所有这些都是<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f9d5f281-3a03-4bfb-935b-67e664cb086f&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Economist&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAefUpRVUl_Xb-2eN0NHHvZMzNr0bumlUqMjPj1n4Zuuy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fbusiness%2F2017%2F06%2F01%2Fchinas-new-cyber-security-law-is-worryingly-vague&amp;uuid=vnv3tha512bJuY980914">2017 年《中国互联网安全法》</a>的一部分。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>苹果成功地置身于竞争之外，可能是因为富士康和该国其他供应商雇佣了数百万人。它还遵循中国的法律，删除了数千个VPN等非法应用程序。然而，它也比其他公司更容易受到攻击。除了对制造业的依赖之外，中国的收入约占苹果总收入的 19%。</p><p>在美国对华为和其他中国公司实施禁令后，北京也对芯片制造商美光科技<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beijing-bans-chinese-companies-from-using-micron-chips-in-critical-infrastructure-183039607.html">实施了</a>类似的禁运。本周早些时候，故事发生了进一步的转折，当时中国电子公司华为发布了 Mate 60 Pro 智能手机，该智能手机采用 7 纳米国产芯片<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/teardown-huaweis-new-phone-shows-chinas-chip-breakthrough-2023-09-04/">，经拆解发现</a>比预期更先进。在与美国持续实施贸易制裁后，中国还为其芯片行业设立了 400 亿美元的基金。</p><p>特斯拉是另一家容易受到中国政策变化影响的美国公司。据报道，中国在第一季度的销量中占据了<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-hit-record-quarterly-sales-china-even-market-share-shrinks-analysts-2023-06-28/">很大一部分</a>，并且它是唯一一家在 2023 年上半年获得市场份额的外国汽车制造商。中国最近<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAR7ljjg0Z4gxjsSyitLLeYmluoSsSAdB3ez_tfemVoiQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchina-to-restrict-tesla-usage-by-military-and-state-personnel-11616155643%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-to-restrict-tesla-usage-by-military-and-state-personnel-11616155643?mod=article_inline">限制</a>军人和国有企业员工使用特斯拉汽车据<em>《华尔街</em>日报》早些时候报道，公司。</p><p>苹果将​​在不到一周的时间内发布 iPhone 15，据报道，该机将配备更薄的边框、钛金属框架、USB-C 充电等功能。苹果尚未对此事做出回应，但 Engadget 已联系该公司征求意见。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/china-intensizes-its-crackdown-on-officials-using-iphones-132419856.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/china-intensifies-its-crackdown-on-officials-using-iphones-132419856.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c0c02e69-dd19-4084-bcac-0b373fa80cea</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 13:24:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694011493</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T14:45:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="3345" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/ad5380f0-4cb0-11ee-bdb5-8ab35472944d" width="4975"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3345" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/ad5380f0-4cb0-11ee-bdb5-8ab35472944d" width="4975"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Photo taken on Aug. 14, 2023 shows iPhones at an Apple store in Hangzhou, East China's Zhejiang province. On the same day, data released by TechInsights showed that Apple's iPhone sales in China surpassed the United States for the first time in the second quarter of 2023, becoming the largest single market for iPhone shipments. (Photo by Costfoto/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[China Became The Largest Market For iPhone Shipments]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA['Slack AI' will summarize your work chat starting this winter]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>继今年早些时候在纽约世界巡回赛上<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/slack-is-getting-in-on-the-gpt-ai-trend-090054594.html">推出</a>为 Slack 开发的生成式人工智能功能后，Salesforce 在其<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.salesforce.com/dreamforce/">Dreamforce</a>公告中透露，它现在正准备在今年冬天试用这些新功能。 Slack AI（这些功能的统称）内置于平台中，以便于访问。它的功能之一是立即生成频道亮点，可以立即告诉用户对话中最重要的部分，然后他们可以将其用于报告或简单地阅读他们可能错过的内容。</p><p>对于那些只想了解特定对话要点而不是整个频道的人来说，Slack AI 还可以一键生成话题摘要。如上图所示，人工智能生成的摘要不仅包含亮点，还列出了用户可以根据对话中人们发布的疑虑、评论和建议采取的后续步骤。此外，当人们在平台上搜索信息时，Slack AI 可以给出详尽的答案。目前，在 Slack 上搜索只能显示带有关键字的消息、文件和频道，但 Slack AI 可以将所有这些信息包装在一个带有摘要的包中，使它们更易于解析。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Salesforce 发布最新公告是在其开始为其以业务为中心的消息应用程序<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/slacks-latest-redesign-has-a-dedicated-dm-tab-and-a-discord-style-activity-view-130032154.html">推出</a>新外观近一个月后发布的。重新设计的界面旨在消除可能分散某些人注意力的杂乱，从而帮助用户更加集中注意力。例如，Slack 的新侧边栏将用户的所有工作区折叠成一个图块，并添加了“主页”、“私信”和“活动”按钮，以及“搜索”和“创建”按钮。专用的 DM 选项卡列出了用户的私人聊天，并允许他们预览每个对话的最新消息，而无需打开它。如果用户想摆脱更多混乱，还可以打开一个选项，仅查看未读消息。</p><p>该公司预计将在其 Dreamforce 活动中透露更多有关 Slack AI 和其他新产品的信息，该活动将于 9 月 12 日至 9 月 14 日举行，并将在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.salesforce.com/plus">Salesforce+</a>上直播。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/slack-ai-will-summarize-your-work-chat-starting-this-winter-130046724.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/slack-ai-will-summarize-your-work-chat-starting-this-winter-130046724.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5d90f48b-bbdd-4796-bbbb-022fd47e846a</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 13:00:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694002414</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T12:13:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1015" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6e637d00-4ca6-11ee-8f67-35e9d336fb63" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1015" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6e637d00-4ca6-11ee-8f67-35e9d336fb63" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Slack]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A screenshot showing the Slack interface with a note on its new AI capabilities.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Slack AI]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to find the best gaming console for you in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>没有“最好的视频游戏机”这样的东西，但找出哪一款最适合您想要的游戏体验是更容易实现的。有七个系统可以合理地称为“当前一代”，而其他系统，例如 Valve 的 Steam Deck，则进一步搅浑了水。 Engadget 的员工几乎可以在您能想到的所有游戏机上玩游戏，还有一些您可能<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-30-atari-lynx-30-year-anniversary.html">已经很久</a>没有考虑过的游戏机了。</p><p>对于一些游戏玩家来说，只有最高规格的系统才可以。其他人只需要以最便宜的方式玩最新的游戏；也许您更看重便携性；或者您可能已经多年没有玩过游戏，正在寻找一款最适合家人一起享受的系统。游戏机有无数的用例，这就是我们撰写这篇文章的原因。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>我们已经审查和评估了这里的每台游戏机，有些游戏机不止一次，并尝试根据特定需求对“最佳游戏机”进行分类。您会在这里找到 10 个精选，其中包括所有大玩家，以及两个最佳“高端游戏机”，每个都有不同的原因。我们希望在读完本指南后，您将更接近决定选择具有完美规格和功能的控制台。</p><h2>最佳高端游戏机：PS5</h2><p><core-commerce id="f54dfe7021d1424bacded4848470c144" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GameStop;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ffe106af-8248-4af3-9098-a2d4fd637766&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GameStop&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeUGezdyXhQwWAY0O_Wad3FVwWP87zACzb6Zur-48eLS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamestop.com%2Fconsoles-hardware%2Fplaystation-5%2Fconsoles%2Fproducts%2Fsony-playstation-5-console%2F11108140.html">PlayStation 5</a>提供当前一代游戏机中最令人惊叹的图形和无缝性能。索尼坚持 PS5 的传统硬件升级周期，与上一代相比显着提高了处理能力和视觉保真度，并推出了充满沉浸式机制的新游戏手柄。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9EdWFsU2Vuc2UtV2lyZWxlc3MtQ29udHJvbGxlci1QbGF5U3RhdGlvbi01L2RwL0IwOEZDNkM3NVk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQ4JhfboL0XrldAS9pA6OlemuhP0Wc5ayVyagUEci7x2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDualSense-Wireless-Controller-PlayStation-5%2Fdp%2FB08FC6C75Y">DualSense</a>是索尼最新的控制器，具有出色的功能：它沿着手柄提供强烈而精确的触觉反馈，并具有自适应触发器，这意味着 R2 和 L2 按钮的张力会随着玩家装备各种武器和工具而变化。这是 Xbox 系列游戏机根本不具备的。</p><p>与此同时，PS5 提供了一系列主机独占游戏，包括<em>《战神：诸神黄昏》</em> 、 <em>《归来》</em> 、 <em>《恶魔之魂》</em>重制版、Insomniac 的蜘蛛侠系列、每一款<em>《最后生还者》</em>游戏和重新发行的游戏，以及一系列《最终幻想》游戏。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:PlayStation;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0f845666-5cc0-42c7-863d-d873ae1b6087&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=PlayStation&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZjg0NTY2Ni01Y2MwLTQyYzctODYzZC1kODczYWUxYjYwODciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucGxheXN0YXRpb24uY29tL2VuLXVzL3BzLXBsdXMvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhNjA1ZDc0NS1mNTQyLTQ0ZDAtYmZmNy0zZGE5YmMwZTg3NDAifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdjkii3KgcxDuw2nUj5Qg9PVudYh5KkEe8dEKkH5BCce&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fps-plus%2F">PlayStation Plus Premium</a>是索尼每月订阅服务的最高级别，增加了云流媒体、免费赠品和可供随时下载的游戏目录。 Premium 的价格为每月 18 美元或每年 120 美元，Plus 生态系统中还有更便宜的套餐，福利也更少。</p><p> PS5 放在电视旁边可能看起来有点<em>滑稽</em>，但实际上，重要的是它的内部结构。嘿，这就是<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:dbrand;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b4b2716f-3984-4476-b619-18c9cba6b899&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=dbrand&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJiNGIyNzE2Zi0zOTg0LTQ0NzYtYjYxOS0xOGM5Y2JhNmI4OTkiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9kYnJhbmQuY29tL3Nob3Avc3BlY2lhbC1lZGl0aW9uL3BzNT9jYXRlZ29yeT1kaXNjIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhNjA1ZDc0NS1mNTQyLTQ0ZDAtYmZmNy0zZGE5YmMwZTg3NDAifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXMB4j7CaWDh_wxBv4Iy10GD_jYGF36Qi9nFQ2cFWdwx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fdbrand.com%2Fshop%2Fspecial-edition%2Fps5%3Fcategory%3Ddisc">dbrand 这样的</a>公司存在的原因。 <em>– 杰西卡·康迪特，高级记者</em></p><h2>最佳高端游戏机：Xbox Series X</h2><p><core-commerce id="d491936f75d64483a1cf5d7e3abdcec6" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAc072dhIRRzDY0onNNRbNkAAPX9DxH7zu9gyPSIdOT2i&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXbox-X%2Fdp%2FB08H75RTZ8">Xbox Series X</a>是市场上功能最强大的游戏机，再加上<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Xbox;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5f41950e-8ca3-4481-8466-a22b28b80e32&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Xbox&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZjQxOTUwZS04Y2EzLTQ0ODEtODQ2Ni1hMjJiMjhiODBlMzIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueGJveC5jb20vZW4tVVMveGJveC1nYW1lLXBhc3MiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVvIL8LgGNKPwAb1IjZmE-d_9mtPgypHn-bbCJaYFzzv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fxbox-game-pass">Game Pass 订阅</a>，它为您提供了几乎无穷无尽的游戏库（包括微软发布日发布的游戏）。虽然我们仍然希望在 Xbox 上看到更多独占游戏，但<em>《Starfield》</em> 、 <em>《Redfall》</em>和改版的<em>《Forza Motor Sport》</em>等主要游戏也即将推出。 PC 游戏玩家还可能喜欢 Windows 和 Xbox 游戏之间的交叉购买，以及使用 Game Pass 从云传输游戏的能力。当然，索尼仍然控制着大预算叙事游戏，但微软平台上的丰富产品——包括小型独立游戏、经典特许经营游戏和 EA Play 提供的大量精彩游戏（包含在 PC 和 Ultimate 的 Game Pass 中）——令人震惊。</p><p>过去，你必须坚持使用所有朋友都在使用的同一台游戏机，但如今，大多数游戏都支持跨平台多人游戏，这使得这种考虑变得毫无意义。如果您想与朋友一起玩<em>《使命召唤》</em> ，那么您购买的是 Xbox Series X 还是 PlayStation 5 并不重要。那么现在最好的建议是什么？根据您想玩的独占游戏以及潜在的订阅权益进行选择。如果您想了解《士官长》的下一步走向，或者只是厌倦了为第一方游戏和一些独立游戏支付全价，那么 Series X 和 Game Pass 可能是您最满意的选择。 <em>– 德文德拉·哈达瓦尔，高级记者</em></p><h2>最佳预算游戏机：Xbox Series S + Game Pass</h2><p><core-commerce id="dcf4641a7cc1405b9a14ea7e0478b08d" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAS5tvXXcxcwzqSc_8BjIFCPFrrzKNgDPICXIq19zzS0L&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXbox-S%2Fdp%2FB08G9J44ZN&amp;uuid=KoI0joQIoP6aSaY034405">Xbox Series S</a>拥有足够的性能来玩最新、最棒的游戏，但它作为半便携式 Game Pass 机器确实非常出色。 S 系列是一款紧凑型控制台，没有磁盘驱动器，通常售价为 300 美元（尽管它的售价经常为 250 至 270 美元）。这个长方形的小宝贝可以玩高于 1080p 分辨率的游戏，但不会达到 4K，而且整体性能不如 Series X。Series S 的存储空间也比它的大兄弟少，这是它的主要缺点。</p><p>这就是<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5f41950e-8ca3-4481-8466-a22b28b80e32&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Xbox&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZjQxOTUwZS04Y2EzLTQ0ODEtODQ2Ni1hMjJiMjhiODBlMzIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueGJveC5jb20vZW4tVVMveGJveC1nYW1lLXBhc3MiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVvIL8LgGNKPwAb1IjZmE-d_9mtPgypHn-bbCJaYFzzv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fxbox-game-pass&amp;uuid=rJnJyduzKPr74PXO35405">Game Pass 的</a>用武之地。 Game Pass Ultimate 订阅可解锁 S 系列（以及 PC 和移动设备）上的云流媒体，让玩家无需下载任何内容即可进入大型库。 <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9YYm94LUdhbWUtUGFzcy1VbHRpbWF0ZS1NZW1iZXJzaGlwL2RwL0IwN1RGUDdKRkg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAV_8HsqXau2D06e0n4d-xpzuWuz4zl4xswxRPRm6dWYL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXbox-Game-Pass-Ultimate-Membership%2Fdp%2FB07TFP7JFH&amp;uuid=0ihVoXTSUHONDJBe36405">Game Pass Ultimate 的价格为每月 15 美元</a>，第一个月为 1 美元。微软拥有业界最可靠的云网络，并致力于在 Game Pass 的第一天发布所有 Xbox Game Studios 的大型新游戏。索尼尚未在内部发布 PlayStation Plus 时做出这样的承诺。</p><p>即使没有 Game Pass，Series S 也是参与 Xbox 主机生态系统的最便宜的方式，并且它可以玩 Series X 可以玩的所有游戏。您可能只需要随时删除下载的内容即可。 <em>– JC</em></p><h2>最适合本地多人游戏：Nintendo Switch</h2><p><core-commerce id="4ee91e8e655441e8a602280abef0bf8f" data-type="product-list"></p><p>遗憾的是，在线多人游戏的兴起意味着大多数游戏机的本地选择的消亡——也就是说，除了<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfHWbvZ3H4BVL5-__W3Ql06J0eBlri8QkH9GvPXFLhvz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNintendo-SwitchTM-Neon-Blue-Joy%25E2%2580%2591ConTM-Switch%2Fdp%2FB0BFJWCYTL%2F">任天堂 Switch</a>之外。这归功于任天堂的传统：这家公司始终优先考虑与朋友和家人在沙发上玩耍的简单之美。无论是四位玩家在<em>《马里奥赛车》</em>中本地对战，还是在<em>《马里奥派对》</em>中投入各种迷你游戏，只需连接到电视的一个 Switch，您就可以享受到乐趣。连接其他控制器让你的朋友加入是轻而易举的事——如果他们有自己的 Switch，他们很可能就拥有这样的东西。由于它是一款便携式游戏机，您可以随时通过本地网络与其他人对战，让您享受与朋友在一起的美妙体验，同时还拥有自己的私人屏幕。尝试用 PS5 来实现这一点。 <em>– DH</em></p><h2>最佳便携式沙发：Valve Steam Deck</h2><p><core-commerce id="14c693a28cf142a082456ba805bafc95" data-type="product-list"></p><p>主要在家中使用的便携式游戏机的想法可能会让人觉得违反直觉，但这实际上是很多人喜欢玩视频游戏的方式，而<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://store.steampowered.com/steamdeck">Steam Deck</a>帮助证明了这一点。 Steam Deck 于 2022 年 2 月推出，并迅速成为一款流行的 PC 便携式电脑，适合那些想要远离办公桌而不是 Steam 图书馆的人们。这是一款厚重的手持游戏机，配有双模拟摇杆和触控板；标准面部按钮、缓冲器和触发器；四个后答题器和一个 7 英寸液晶触摸屏。它<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/steam-deck-review-small-hands-180026719.html">很大而且非常漂亮</a>，可以很好地玩大多数电脑游戏。</p><p> Steam Deck 起价 400 美元，最高价 650 美元，在<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/handheld-gaming-pc-retro-indie-handhelds-steam-deck-playdate-150038001.html">PC 便携式设备</a>领域相对实惠。 Steam Deck 有点太大并且耗电，不适合旅行时随身携带，但它非常适合依偎在客厅的沙发上 - 附近有一个支撑枕头和电源插座。 <em>– JC</em></p><h2>最适合初次玩游戏的玩家：Nintendo Switch Lite</h2><p><core-commerce id="415ae8f5dae14df49c37aedd22b5f1cb" data-type="product-list"></p><p>任天堂有着制造类似坦克的便携式游戏机的历史， <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9OaW50ZW5kby1Td2l0Y2gtTGl0ZS1CbHVlL2RwL0IwOTJWVDFKR0Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeJyPYLs3KmIeIWKy3q0sgGuVHaOVdgPGgNqqeIyd729&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNintendo-Switch-Lite-Blue%2Fdp%2FB092VT1JGD&amp;uuid=4TYsim5VjU5AQwD646407">Switch Lite</a>也不例外。它的速度与其较大的兄弟产品一样快，但由于它具有集成控制功能，因此您不必担心如果它掉落，任何 Joy-cons 会飞走。 Switch Lite 的 5.5 英寸屏幕和较小的边框总是让小手更容易握持，我发现这一点特别有用，因为我四岁的女儿终于开始玩电子游戏了。 Switch 上提供了各种各样适合儿童的内容，但我们建议您通过控制台的在线服务深入了解任天堂的经典游戏。孩子们最终会自己弄清楚<em>《我的世界》</em> ，但需要老一代人通过<em>《超级马里奥兄弟 3》</em>灌输适当平台游戏的价值。 <em>– DH</em></p><h2>最适合通勤的手持游戏机：Nintendo Switch Lite</h2><p><core-commerce id="784ad30f7f884dfd87c26bc3a7128d40" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9OaW50ZW5kby1Td2l0Y2gtTGl0ZS1CbHVlL2RwL0IwOTJWVDFKR0Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbGUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeJyPYLs3KmIeIWKy3q0sgGuVHaOVdgPGgNqqeIyd729&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNintendo-Switch-Lite-Blue%2Fdp%2FB092VT1JGD">Switch Lite</a>是迄今为止市场上最可爱的手持游戏机，这只是它非常适合在公共场合使用的原因之一。 The Switch Lite is a tiny, lightweight handheld with a 5.5 inch LCD touchscreen and basic gamepad buttons, and it&#39;s sold in a variety of colorways and special editions. It feels natural to pull out while on the bus, riding the subway, in a waiting room, or just hanging out at a cafe, bar or park. It&#39;s a low-profile portable that offers a library of engaging games from Nintendo and beyond, including exclusive franchises like The Legend of Zelda, Pokemon, Mario Kart, Smash Bros., Bayonetta, Animal Crossing and Kirby.</p><p> In comparison to the standard Switch, the Lite model is sturdier for everyday commutes because it doesn&#39;t have detachable controllers and it takes up less space in your bag. It&#39;s also about $150 cheaper than the larger <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfHWbvZ3H4BVL5-__W3Ql06J0eBlri8QkH9GvPXFLhvz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNintendo-SwitchTM-Neon-Blue-Joy%25E2%2580%2591ConTM-Switch%2Fdp%2FB0BFJWCYTL%2F">Switch</a> , at $200. <em>– JC</em></p><h2> Best for air travel: Nintendo Switch</h2><p><core-commerce id="38f7059a338547dbb6af1f6a7f951648" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfHWbvZ3H4BVL5-__W3Ql06J0eBlri8QkH9GvPXFLhvz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNintendo-SwitchTM-Neon-Blue-Joy%25E2%2580%2591ConTM-Switch%2Fdp%2FB0BFJWCYTL%2F">Switch&#39;s</a> hardware may be showing its age, but it&#39;s still the best way to get some gaming in during long flights. Having a 6.2-inch screen (or 7-inches with the pricier Switch OLED) in your hands makes it easy to ignore annoying seat neighbors, countless delays and all of the other indignities of air travel. The Switch should also survive for several hours of gameplay, and it&#39;s easy to charge for longer journeys. While the Steam Deck may be tempting, it&#39;s also so large it&#39;ll likely fill up much of your backpack. The Switch can still fit alongside your computer and other gear, and its game library is so vast, you&#39;ll never be left wanting for things to play. <em>– DH</em></p><h2> Best retro gaming console for nostalgia: Retroid Pocket 3</h2><p><core-commerce id="2ef0b3c14bd24a3eb080346fdf950033" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVsnRqtesX7qDfs4kLbW-WqJzsbmsnuUUYD3njwurA23&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRetroid-Pocket-Handheld-Multiple-Emulators%2Fdp%2FB0B8S9GH8T">Retroid Pocket 3</a> is an accessible, streamlined <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/retroid-pocket-3-irl-153508438.html">emulation machine</a> that&#39;s capable of handling games from the sixth generation down – that&#39;s anything up to the GameCube and PlayStation 2. It can even run some PSP games, apparently, but at this point, you&#39;re just getting greedy. The Retroid Pocket 3 brings classics like <em>Super Mario RPG</em> , <em>Metal Gear Solid</em> , <em>Final Fantasy IX</em> and so many others to modern audiences, and they all look better than ever.</p><p> What&#39;s more, the Retroid Pocket 3 is an Android-based handheld gaming console, which means it also works as a hub for cloud streaming through services like Xbox Game Pass Ultimate. This little device is tinier than a Switch Lite and it has a 4.7 inch LCD touchscreen – that&#39;s smaller than Nintendo&#39;s latest handheld but bigger than the screen of a classic Game Boy, for what it&#39;s worth. What&#39;s most astonishing about the Retroid Pocket 3 is its price: just $150. <em>– JC</em></p><h2> <strong>Best console with a large streaming game library: Xbox Series X (or S)</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="fa2f574ddd614f9080c238640353a1f1" data-type="product-list"></p><p> For console gamers, <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Xbox;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5f41950e-8ca3-4481-8466-a22b28b80e32&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Xbox&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZjQxOTUwZS04Y2EzLTQ0ODEtODQ2Ni1hMjJiMjhiODBlMzIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueGJveC5jb20vZW4tVVMveGJveC1nYW1lLXBhc3MiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImE2MDVkNzQ1LWY1NDItNDRkMC1iZmY3LTNkYTliYzBlODc0MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVvIL8LgGNKPwAb1IjZmE-d_9mtPgypHn-bbCJaYFzzv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fxbox-game-pass">Microsoft&#39;s Game Pass subscription</a> has been a revelation. For $10 a month, you can play hundreds of games, including all of Microsoft&#39;s first-party software, as well as major titles like <em>Monster Hunter Rise</em> and <em>A Plague Tale Requiem</em> . Even better, Microsoft-owned titles are available the day they&#39;re released! Bump up to the $15 Game Pass Ultimate tier and you&#39;ll also get access to cloud gaming, which lets you stream select titles to your phone, computer and even some TVs. The sheer variety of content on Game Pass makes it hard to stomach paying full price for a game ever again.</p><p> Sony&#39;s response to Game Pass amounts to an evolution of its <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:PlayStation;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0f845666-5cc0-42c7-863d-d873ae1b6087&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=PlayStation&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZjg0NTY2Ni01Y2MwLTQyYzctODYzZC1kODczYWUxYjYwODciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucGxheXN0YXRpb24uY29tL2VuLXVzL3BzLXBsdXMvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhNjA1ZDc0NS1mNTQyLTQ0ZDAtYmZmNy0zZGE5YmMwZTg3NDAifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdjkii3KgcxDuw2nUj5Qg9PVudYh5KkEe8dEKkH5BCce&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fps-plus%2F">PlayStation Plus service</a> . Its highest-tier &quot;Premium&quot; offering costs $18 a month, and it also gives you access to a large library of titles and cloud streaming. <em>But</em> , Sony isn&#39;t adding first-party titles to any PS Plus tier the day they launch — you&#39;ll either have to pay full price, or wait until they get added to the rotation. Until Sony caves, having release day access to titles makes Game Pass the obviously better subscription service. <em>– DH</em></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-console-140057674.html?src=rss]]>;</description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-console-140057674.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a605d745-f542-44d0-bff7-3da9bc0e8740</guid><dc:creator>恩杰特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 06 Sep 2023 13:00:31 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694005232</ingested><modified> 2023-09-06T13:00:40+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Consoles]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Engadget]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/c5cb9bf0-010d-11eb-bfe7-d9590b988708" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="930" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/232c17d0-ae12-11ed-b7d7-59ba2b781c46" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Sony PlayStation 5 Microsoft Xbox Series X]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Sony PlayStation 5 Microsoft Xbox Series X]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[GoPro announces Hero 12 Black with AirPods support and better battery life]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Today, GoPro unveils its latest camera: The Hero 12 Black. This time around, the updates are mostly on the user experience, with a slight focus on pro users and creators. Perhaps the most exciting new “feature” for regular GoPro users will be the claimed extended battery life. The company says “Up to two times” the runtime of previous cameras. Battery life has long been a pain point, so we&#39;ll be keen to see what that looks like in real terms.</p><p> There are some new shooting modes, with 8:7 (full sensor) recording now available across the board, including TimeWarp and the Night Effect modes for the first time. Recording in 8:7 allows you to “punch out” different aspect ratio content from the same source material while maintaining a high resolution. The camera&#39;s HDR mode has also been tuned for even better handling of mixed lighting conditions. Hypersmooth, GoPro&#39;s in-camera stabilization is now on its sixth iteration —- but it&#39;s been solid right from the start, so we&#39;re interested to see what difference this makes in practice.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> For the pros (or the aspiring ones) two new additions will be of particular interest. First there&#39;s “GP-Log” which is GoPro&#39;s take on logarithmic shooting mode — which makes color grading in post much more flexible. Secondly, there&#39;s the addition of Timecode Sync, so if you&#39;re recording with multiple GoPro Hero 12&#39;s, they can easily be synchronized for airtight edits in post.</p><p> As for creators, again there&#39;s a brace of updates that will be of interest. Interestingly, the Hero 12 Black now works with Bluetooth headsets for both playback and recording — including AirPods. Now, videos can use Bluetooth headphone microphones which can be blended with the in-camera mic recordings as you wish. You can even use your headset to use GoPro&#39;s voice activation, opening the door for more creative shots taken without having to be near the camera or use the app/remote accessory. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/f2bb4970-4ca1-11ee-bddf-a97c22c2d15f" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/f2bb4970-4ca1-11ee-bddf-a97c22c2d15f" style="height:1333px;width:2000px;" alt="The underside of the new GoPro Hero 12 Black shows the new built-in  tripod mount." data-uuid="c025459d-0888-3e94-803b-3efd8dfecb62"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Photo by James Trew / Engadget</div></figure><p> The second creator-friendly feature is vertical capture. You&#39;ve always been able to hold a GoPro at 90 degrees, and on later models the menus would also rotate for ease of use. This time around, you can simply activate vertical mode even while the camera is mounted horizontally. It takes advantage of the new sensor introduced with the Hero 11 that&#39;s big enough to punch out a full 9:16 vertical video at 4K/30FPS without having to re-mount or re-orient the camera.</p><p> If it&#39;s important to you for other people to know you have the newest camera, this year that&#39;ll be a little easier as the Hero 12 Black has a speckled faceplate in a break from the usual monochrome design. But there&#39;s one other physical change that will elicit a small peep of joy from long-time users: The camera now has a regular tripod mount (1/4 inch 20 thread ) built-in on the bottom, nestled right between the fold out mounting fingers. No more adapters needed for all those <em>other</em> camera accessories you might have lying around.</p><p> One last change this time around is that GoPro seems to have dropped the need to sign up for its cloud subscription service to get a better price on the camera — the Hero 12 Black will simply cost $400 for everyone. Pre-orders open today and the camera lands in retail September 13.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/gopro-announces-hero-12-black-with-airpods-support-and-better-battery-life-130027283.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/gopro-announces-hero-12-black-with-airpods-support-and-better-battery-life-130027283.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 91f8419b-d367-49bc-a738-ec0b624129a8</guid><dc:creator> James Trew</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特<